2. L2 REGISTRATION: Commercial deployment of this protocol requires formal 
   registration of the 5-letter L2 segment via smarthomemiles@gmail.com.
3. ETHICAL BOUNDARIES: The hardware must respect the SST-E (Spatial Social 
   Topology and Ethical Boundaries) and must not be used for illicit surveillance.

